> X CANDLE
This candle is a "canonical hour candle". It is used by Brother Cuthbert to tell the hours for offices and when to ring the great bell. It has burned down past 7 marks, leaving 17 marks remaining below the flame. From it, you estimate the time as seven in the morning.

